<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Our internal processes have identified that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">you were overcharged for your insurance policy</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>A refund of £XXXX will be returned to your account within 3-5 working days.<br></b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b><br></b>Apologies for any inconvenience caused and, if you have any questions, please do not hesitate to get in contact on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
